text19 CODE 0 FA6 FA6 3E 1 2
text20 CODE 0 1086 1086 A 1 2
text21 CODE 0 1090 1090 A 1 2
text22 CODE 0 109A 109A A 1 2
text23 CODE 0 105A 105A 14 1 2
nvBANK0 BANK0 1 BD BD 6 1 1
cstackCOMRAM COMRAM 1 1 1 5B 1 1
bssBANK0 BANK0 1 60 60 56 1 1
smallconst SMALLCONST 0 600 600 30 1 2
idataBANK0 CODE 0 10A4 10A4 7 1 1
dataBANK0 BANK0 1 B6 B6 7 1 1
bssCOMRAM COMRAM 1 5C 5C 4 1 1
config CONFIG 4 300000 300000 E 1 1
